Uproar has greeted an incident in karatina, Nyeri county where angry boda boda operators stormed into a hospital dragged out two people and killed them .Alleging that they were members of a gang which had been terrorizing motorcycle operators. This as concern is rising over the impunity displayed by boda boda operators in the country who take matters into their hands. and as Daniel Kariuki reports, the incident is just one among many that calls for stern action to streamline the sector